data.description:
Welcome home! 3 bedroom 2 bathroom STUNNER in Princeton! Immaculate maintenance by the seller, keeping this home in pristine condition. Offering a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for you to come in and make it your very own! Luxury Vinyl plank flooring, granite countertops and a nice open concept allows for perfect gatherings and entertainment. This home has the perfect layout, separating the master bedroom from secondary bedrooms. Property sits in a desirable community offering 3 pools, a splash pad and multiple playgrounds to all community residents. 

Seller will consider a turnkey offer for the right price.
 Refridgerater, Washer and dryer are not included, but can be included in the purchase with a good offer.
